# symbol-counter

Count unique symbols in a string or file.

## Install

```
pip install symbol-counter
```

## Library usage

```python
from symbol_counter import count_symbols

print(count_symbols("test"))
```

## CLI usage

```
symbol-counter --string "aabbc"
```

```
symbol-counter --file path/to/input.txt
```
